photo.title: Succulent at UC Botanical Garden
photo.tags: california canon garden botanical eos rebel bay berkeley san francisco university bigma sigma area monopod xti
photo.description:
UC Berkeley's Botanical Garden. Loved the symmetry.
We went to the UC Berkeley Botanical Garden in the morning, the San Francisco Orchid Festival in the afternoon, then the San Francisco Botanical Garden in Golden Gate park later in the evening. The UC Garden was the most interesting to the adults, and Ben was floored at the variety of Orchid's there are.
